1. *Krećemo* u pet ujutru. (We're starting at five o'clock in the morning.)
2. Uskoro ćemo *kretati* se prema jugu. (We will soon be moving southward.)
3. *Krenuli* smo pravo u najveću avanturu. (We have embarked on the greatest adventure.)
4. *Kreću* velike promene. (Big changes are coming.)
5. *Krenula* je bitka. (The battle has begun.)